Start or switch to Moonlight:startmoon.sh
Stop Moonlight:stopmoon.sh force
Restart Moonlight:restartmoon.sh force
Install Moonlight:confapps_ph.sh -p int -a Moonlight
Uninstall Moonlight:confapps_ph.sh -p rem -a Moonlight
Configure Moonlight (pair and set all options):confapps_ph.sh -p conf -a Moonlight
List all Moonlight shared games:listmoon_ph.sh
List all available options for Moonlight:confopts_ph.sh -p list -a Moonlight
View the current value of Moonlight option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Moonlight -g
View the current value of Moonlight option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Moonlight -g -r
Change the value of read-write Moonlight option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Moonlight -s
Change the value of read-write Moonlight option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Moonlight -s -r
Display help for Moonlight option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Moonlight -d
Display help for Moonlight option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Moonlight -d -r
Display TTY currently allocated to Moonlight:confapps_ph.sh -p tty -a Moonlight
Move Moonlight to another TTY:confapps_ph.sh -p move -a Moonlight -t prompt
Return to previous menu:return
